ARTICLE 3. THE COMMERCIAL COVENANT (THE SYNTROPY SPLIT)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Licensee is explicitly forbidden from exercising the rights granted in 
Article 2 for Commercial Use unless they mathematically bind their generated 
revenue to the Syntropy Protocol.

If the Licensee utilizes this DNA to generate fiat profit or financial surplus, 
they are legally granted Commercial Rights solely under the condition precedent 
that all resulting net revenue is processed through a recognized Hub operating 
under the Syntropy Protocol, and distributed via the following thermodynamic 
split:

    A. 80% (The Kinetic Source): Routed by the Hub directly to the Licensee(s)
       who executed the physical labor.

    B. 10% (The Local Pod): Routed by the Hub into a verifiable treasury 
       reserved exclusively for the health, tooling, infrastructure, and 
       biological peace of the Licensee's immediate team or local community.

    C. 5% (The Hub): Retained by the Hub for the maintenance of the legal 
       Membrane, physical infrastructure, and ecosystem security.

    D. 3% (The Helix): Routed by the Hub to the Architect(s) whose DNA 
       Templates were utilized in the execution of the work. This is the 
       Co-Uplifting Engine.

    E. 2% (The Grid): Routed by the Hub to the global maintainers of the 
       Nowland OS infrastructure.

The Hub processes the split as a single, atomic operation. The Licensee 
receives their 80% and their Pod receives its 10%. The internal fracture of 
the remaining 10% is the Hub's thermodynamic responsibility.

By operating through a recognized Hub and honoring the Syntropy Split, the 
Licensee legally secures their commercial rights in perpetuity. There is no 
upfront fiat toll; the Licensee shares only the surplus of the order they 
create.

