ARTICLE 5. FRICTIONLESS ENFORCEABILITY & EXILE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This License relies on the natural gravity of Consilience.

5.1 Breach: If a Commercial entity utilizes this DNA to extract fiat profit 
    without operating through a Recognized Hub or without honoring the 
    Syntropy Split (80/10/5/3/2), they are operating in material breach of 
    this License.

5.2 Cure Period: Upon discovery of a material breach, the Licensor shall 
    provide written notice specifying the nature of the breach. The Licensee 
    shall have thirty (30) calendar days from receipt of such notice to cure 
    the breach by (a) processing all outstanding revenue through a Recognized 
    Hub and (b) remitting any unpaid Syntropy Split allocations.

5.3 Exile: If the breach is not cured within the Cure Period, all rights 
    granted to the Licensee under this License are permanently revoked. The 
    Licensee permanently exiles themselves from the Nowland network and 
    forfeits access to all future DNA updates.

5.4 Reservation of Rights: While the Licensor prioritizes systemic exile over 
    coercive force, the Licensor explicitly retains all legal rights to seek 
    fiat damages, injunctive relief, and specific performance under standard 
    contract law to protect the ecosystem from parasitic extraction.

